{"tid":1626421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會：對暴徒的破壞行為予以最強烈譴責","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"58f6959f27e46edf0e9efa54a5e200de46a0fad0","tid":1626421,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"昨日多區發生衝突事件，有示威者破壞工聯會的服務點，工聯會對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n有服務點破壞程度嚴重，未必能即時或數日內修復，對於部分服務未能即時恢復深感抱歉，並對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責，要求政府對暴徒繩之以法。"},{"pid":"84ad455e161edbc752814c2d7d2a9fcb56a666e9","tid":1626421,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484472-20191005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484472-20191005.htm&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=6a68e598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484472-20191005.htm&h=158d30e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484472-20191005.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7fb399261e0dfd9cd5a32910f413345938860661","tid":1626421,"uid":257293,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"裝修有好多種<br />\n其實裝修可以裝成連儂牆<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n貼滿中共紅底黑社會嘅證據<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪，甚至清唔到等佢哋自己換玻璃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102