.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地呢個67暴徒記者會，仲有一個重點，就係話佢地辦事處比人破壞，係因為佢地尋日去咗報名參選，係咁話政府應該要講下點確保區選安全同埋公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟開始吹風想取消選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7d30b0a2c992d4230dbb393073555e3454106c","tid":1626421,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4704395c018f0bb026149143d2eee2f2096ca53","tid":1626421,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58f6959f27e46edf0e9efa54a5e200de46a0fad0","tid":1626421,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"昨日多區發生衝突事件，有示威者破壞工聯會的服務點，工聯會對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n有服務點破壞程度嚴重，未必能即時或數日內修復，對於部分服務未能即時恢復深感抱歉，並對破壞行為予以最強烈譴責，要求政府對暴徒繩之以法。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"暴動始祖話人暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:31:33.000Z","msg":"都未放同胞勿近, 拍馬都追唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73c9408e8f6dd712fa5fc13e353690d0ab7fdb4","tid":1626421,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:37:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48d99a3ada8880b754d8565499c51cb69cca776f","tid":1626421,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"下年都唔會見佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4e2c59888bf77fc508ecc70d48cff431cf88fb","tid":1626421,"uid":17263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:46:26.000Z","msg":"🍍🍍🍍"},{"pid":"5882522ba7c5139782e6c90072410fac06019dec","tid":1626421,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:50:25.000Z","msg":"敵人反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3106f214052d43b9dce4bc691657103e8c1d9d2","tid":16